    We developed an educational package that was designed to be delivered as a whole package to families in our team’s local Sydney Aquarium. It includes a variety of different items each targeted at individuals of different age groups; young primary children (13 and below), young adults (ages 10-18), and adults (ages 18+). Our goal was to create a fun and relevant method to educate the public on what our topic was about, and basics on scientific concepts involving synthetic biology and ecology. These items were designed to be interacted with and physically distributed. 
    <br /><br />
