<!-- BOARD GAME -->
<div id="board_game">
    <h2>Board Game: Blue Expanse</h2>
    <br />

    <p>
        Blue Expanse is a 2+ player game. With a target audience of young adults to adults, our objective was to illustrate the building of a healthy reef ecosystem despite various environmental challenges. In doing so, the players learn about the foundational role microorganisms have in ensuring higher order organisms' shelter and food. Each player manages their own reef, across three different periods facing worsening ecological challenges culminating in a mass coral bleaching event. Victory is counted by the sum of final victory points (VP) each player has, with the player scoring the most being the winner. 
    </p>

    <p>
        The creation of the board game was influenced by various popular games, including Dominion, Monopoly, Twilight Struggle, Pandemic and War of Omens. This enabled the game to be better balanced and have greater clarity of mechanisms.
    </p>
